* “发展才是硬道理。”<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":3" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=邓小平南巡讲话：居然有两句话不敢登|url=https://news.boxun.com/news/gb/z_special/2015/09/201509180746.shtml|accessdate=2019-11-06|author=|date=|format=|work=|publisher=博讯|language=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191106045523/https://news.boxun.com/news/gb/z_special/2015/09/201509180746.shtml|archive-date=2019-11-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>
